## Proposed Changes

### Database Layer

#### [NEW] [users_migrations_005.sql](file:///c:/Users/misal/OneDrive/Documents/next-framer/db/schemas/users_migrations_005.sql)

Add a `user_settings` table to store per-user preferences:

```sql
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS user_settings (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY REFERENCES users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    show_profile_on_public BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT FALSE,
    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);
```

- `show_profile_on_public` — the toggle. When `TRUE`, the user's name replaces "You" on their public cards, and hovering reveals the profile card to anyone.

