### Frontend — New Components

#### [NEW] [UserProfileHoverCard.tsx](file:///c:/Users/misal/OneDrive/Documents/next-framer/components/vault/UserProfileHoverCard.tsx)

A hover-triggered popup (using `onMouseEnter`/`onMouseLeave` with a delay) that renders:

- **Header:** User avatar (initial-based), name, "Member since" date
- **Stats grid:** Total items, passwords, notes, snippets, tags — each with an animated count-up
- **Activity graph:** A 12-week bar chart (built with pure SVG, no library) showing weekly item creation. Bars animate in with staggered framer-motion. Accent-colored bars with a gradient fill.
- **Glassmorphism styling** consistent with the vault design system
- Uses `trpc.vault.getUserProfile.useQuery()` — fetches lazily only when the popover opens

