## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
```bash
# Run the migration
node db/run-schemas.mjs

# Verify the dev server compiles without errors
yarn dev
```

### Manual Verification
1. Open Settings modal from sidebar → toggle "Show profile on public items" ON
2. Create a public item → verify the badge shows your name instead of "You"
3. Open an incognito window → hover over your name badge on a public item → verify the animated profile card appears with stats and activity graph
4. Toggle the setting OFF → verify badge goes back to "You" and hover card no longer appears for other users
